{"tid":2091882,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch]集合啦！動物森友會｜動物之森討論區(427) 動森樓海鮮酒家","createTime":"2020-07-03T02:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T12:56:10.000Z","uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fddf4b46f058f0d54d4913da5608c4a77edfcfbd","tid":2091882,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1001開post時希望可以copy埋置頂</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">(用依個留言右上角三點可以 「以此內容建立新主題」，用網頁版可以的話copy埋置頂嗰堆，</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">用電話開post置頂內容會爆字數，可以留言叫巴絲幫手post返)</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/528ykNe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F528ykNe.gif&h=442ae26c&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">置頂</span>有實用資訊</strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/528ykNe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F528ykNe.gif&h=442ae26c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xijn341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXijn341.jpg&h=b1337394&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">買game前你可能會想知 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：隻game玩乜？<br />\nA：比較休閒嘅第二人生。隻game時間係跟現實時間，亦慶祝現實節日例如聖誕，復活節等等。遊戲著重你同動物森民嘅交流互動(隻隻都有自己性格)，慢慢一齊生活 了解對方 成為密友， 同埋裝飾你間屋＆島。今隻主題係無人荒島，新增合成元素，你要由零開始<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">還債</span></span></del>建設你心目中嘅理想小島。遊戲節奏比較輕鬆，預你日日開來玩一陣，啱玩嘅可以玩幾年都得。<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩版先有中文？唔同版本可唔可以連機？<br />\nA：乜版都有 。可以<br />\n<br />\nQ：Online 玩咩？<br />\nA：去朋友／網友座島度一齊hea，一齊砌野，一齊炒<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">股票</span></span></del><br />\n<br />\nQ：單機會唔會無咁好玩？<br />\nA：唔會，隻game係單機game，主要都係著重起你同動物之間嘅交流互動同埋打理你座島。不過多人連機時一樣有野玩咁解。<br />\n<br />\nQ：對手掣好靚，有無得單買？<br />\nA：暫時只見日本My Nintendo Store有得買，但係...<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">更新: 原來已更新可以用PayPal俾錢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：可唔可以用返以前啲Amiibo？<br />\nA：可以。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFFWQrY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFFWQrY.png&h=8c46d7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">圖片來源 YouTube -&gt; rEB1vlAiVxE</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nQ：買game實體定下載版好？有無黃店推介？<br />\nA：隻game預你日日開來玩一陣 實係下載版好，仲唔怕會益<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>代理</strong></span></span>，真係要買實體我會建議你幫襯黃店買水貨。Read: 黃藍黑Game舖大集合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：同一部機唔同user save係共通？<br />\nA：一部機全部user都係住同一個島。<br />\n<br />\nQ：一機多人玩係點？<br />\nA：只有1P可以推展遊戲進度，2P只係執下素材咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無得Cloud Save／轉移個save去第二部機部度？<br />\nA：無。但官方講法係「Online會員專用壞機／唔見機時尋回save file功能開發中」＆「動森專用 機對機save轉移功能開發中」 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好反智</span></span>undefined)<br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩動物村民？<br />\nA：今集總共有近400隻。歷代全角色(好多頁): <a href=\"https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanimalcrossing.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FCategory%3ACharacters&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=065eb753\" target=\"_blank\">https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">特別版主機</span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">入手請幫襯UNY/APITA/AEON/豐澤</span></strong> (唔經代理拎貨)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/animal_crossing_new_horizons/set/img/img-main-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Fanimal_crossing_new_horizons%2Fset%2Fimg%2Fimg-main-06.jpg&h=56e37b2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd3096a474a7d3df26b56bd283c9171274d69e4d","tid":2091882,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">遊戲初期常見問題Q&amp;A // 實用網站 // <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n&bull;由於<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>較時間玩(TT，時間旅人...)</strong></span>增加太多不確定因素，出現任何bug恕各巴絲愛莫能助<br />\n&bull;Post<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">超長交易list</span></strong>時請用<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>五重引用</strong></span>(如下)，以免影響討論<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">[quote][quote][quote][quote][quote]\n內容\n[/quote][/quote][/quote][/quote][/quote]</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">An/iOS 「Nintendo Switch Online」app</span></span><br />\n<em><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">可以scan設計QR code，連機時可以快速打字傾計</span></span></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znca\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nintendo.znca&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=b3effa79\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znca</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/nintendo-switch-online/id1234806557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fnintendo-switch-online%2Fid1234806557&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=b6eb5c19\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/nintendo-switch-online/id1234806557</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">遊戲初期常見問題Q&amp;A</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><em>希望新手問問題前可以望一望先</em></span></span><br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://pastebin.com/raw/BmKPt4dB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2Fraw%2FBmKPt4dB&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=589ad354\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/raw/BmKPt4dB</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQOfd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQOfd2.png&h=e669a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">實用網站</span></span><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">排隊網，計大頭菜價，外島資料，設計pattern，設計主題曲，種花計數機，物品大全</span></span></em><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>股(大頭菜)價計算，留意網頁內指示<br />\n<a href=\"https://mikebryant.github.io/ac-nh-turnip-prices/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmikebryant.github.io%2Fac-nh-turnip-prices%2Findex.html&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=f8a8552d\" target=\"_blank\">https://mikebryant.github.io/ac-nh-turnip-prices/index.html</a><br />\n可以開房俾巴絲排隊，唔駛搞到成個post都係code<br />\n<a href=\"https://turnip.exchange/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fturnip.exchange%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=8de6cab0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://turnip.exchange/</a><br />\n種花計數機<br />\n<a href=\"https://aeonsake.gitlab.io/acnh-flower-breeder/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faeonsake.gitlab.io%2Facnh-flower-breeder%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=1f5dbdfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://aeonsake.gitlab.io/acnh-flower-breeder/</a><br />\n物品大全<br />\n<a href=\"https://nookplaza.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnookplaza.net%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=76b16406\" target=\"_blank\">https://nookplaza.net/</a><br />\n外島旅行攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://wuffs.org/acnh/mysterytour.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwuffs.org%2Facnh%2Fmysterytour.html&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=7d929712\" target=\"_blank\">https://wuffs.org/acnh/mysterytour.html</a><br />\n設計任意pattern，可生成QR code scan落遊戲度，可以匯入任意圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://acpatterns.com/editor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Facpatterns.com%2Feditor&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=42201050\" target=\"_blank\">https://acpatterns.com/editor</a><br />\n分割圖片做幾個正方形，搭上面一齊用效果更佳<br />\n<a href=\"https://pinetools.com/split-image\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpinetools.com%2Fsplit-image&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=127effbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://pinetools.com/split-image</a><br />\n設計主題曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://tunes.nooknet.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftunes.nooknet.net%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=4f5aed77\" target=\"_blank\">https://tunes.nooknet.net/</a><br />\n設計無人島<br />\n<a href=\"https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplanimalcrossing.com%2Fnh%2Fstart%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=bf87842c\" target=\"_blank\">https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">實用圖片／攻略</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaFQNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaFQNo.png&h=47d639d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">真假藝術品</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">，風水攻略，種花攻略，簡易全攻略</span></span></em><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">真假藝術品</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1J-pAxNEnqKlpH7YJuUeKVjxVAvsoujQYjQcmQ8q5VCU/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1J-pAxNEnqKlpH7YJuUeKVjxVAvsoujQYjQcmQ8q5VCU%2Fedit&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=f5ce2dcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1J-pAxNEnqKlpH7YJuUeKVjxVAvsoujQYjQcmQ8q5VCU/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">英文版簡略版全攻略</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-8kQMnmduhraliqCrehaAviG0qlm5BnAb73rPPOf-z0/edit#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-8kQMnmduhraliqCrehaAviG0qlm5BnAb73rPPOf-z0%2Fedit%23&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=971776d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-8kQMnmduhraliqCrehaAviG0qlm5BnAb73rPPOf-z0/edit#</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：風水？<br />\nA：主人房擺唔同顏色家具增加運氣，綠 整體，紅 物品，黃 金錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/FRbfJgYp/fengshui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FFRbfJgYp%2Ffengshui.jpg&h=dc333a39&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thonky.com/animal-crossing-new-leaf/feng-shui-guide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thonky.com%2Fanimal-crossing-new-leaf%2Ffeng-shui-guide&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=937e7626\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thonky.com/animal-crossing-new-leaf/feng-shui-guide</a><br />\n<br />\nＱ：花係咪可以配種？<br />\nＡ：同類花種埋一齊，淋水，側邊有機會出新色花<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xO3uuw5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxO3uuw5.png&h=cea5f2b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqJaQkR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqJaQkR.jpg&h=5f4abd43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<code>source: redd.it/g1vn60  redd.it/g209k5</code><br />\n</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd428ebb609b47e704ff8572bd11a30a69714209","tid":2091882,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:31:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">動森<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">夏日更新第一彈</span></strong> 已於7月3日<ins>早上9點</ins>開始配信！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jO0luDEHesc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjO0luDEHesc&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=a0237e7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jO0luDEHesc</a><br />\n </div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>更新內容</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 下海啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://topics-cdn.nintendo.co.jp/uploads/images/2020/06/8665_02_17114014161544_jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopics-cdn.nintendo.co.jp%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F2020%2F06%2F8665_02_17114014161544_jpg.jpg&h=41f0da93&s=